          Dax Murray is <a href="http://dax.codes">a software engineer by day</a> but <strike>fights demons</strike>
          writes queer fantasy and science fiction by moonlight. Dax writes worlds where being queer is not remarkable,
          and futures are held in the hands of the many instead of the few. Dax studied political science, music, and creative writing at Allegheny College in Meadville, PA. Fey currently resides in Washington, DC with feir cats
          and feir snakes.
          <br/>
          <br/>
