          Dax is a member of the
          <a href="https://krackencollectivebooks.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Kraken Collective.</a>
          The Kraken Collective is an alliance of indie authors who have pooled resources to publish high-quality
          fiction while retaining complete creative control over our stories. We aim to provide a wide variety of
          science fiction and fantasy stories, all starring LGBTQIAP+ characters. From alien hunting lesbians to complex
          political fantasy, The Kraken Collective publishes queer SFF that will blow your mind away and leave you
          craving more.

